            Connect your manufacturing and industrial systems to track energy consumption, production emissions, and operational efficiency in real-time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">What You'll Learn</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-800">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                  </svg>
